{"tid":2200550,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"弄傷婦孺 警指最低武力","createTime":"2020-09-13T05:00:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T06:00:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f3cdcb3bd6705f2eecf77c727d09be8399b58c","tid":2200550,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:00:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/MLH5A6NYSJGTBOCKLXGC3RY6G4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FMLH5A6NYSJGTBOCKLXGC3RY6G4%2F&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513ebr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=5ade760e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200913%2FMLH5A6NYSJGTBOCKLXGC3RY6G4%2F&h=5b286832\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200913/MLH5A6NYSJGTBOCKLXGC3RY6G4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n弄傷婦孺 警指最低武力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/sZhUaWsaznhS54li8YEK1XsJhPM=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MESIMHL26NHKJJUCWFQA3K4TMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FsZhUaWsaznhS54li8YEK1XsJhPM%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMESIMHL26NHKJJUCWFQA3K4TMI.jpg&h=927f411e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■早前有警員在示威現場拉跌孕婦惹起公憤。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方在8月31日及9月6日於九龍區先後襲擊孕婦及女童被輿論炮轟。警方昨日再於facebook回應，聲稱非常重視保護婦女和兒童，一直按嚴格指引及守則處理涉及婦女和兒童的案件，並十分關注有孕婦及未成年人士在示威現場受傷。惟警方指有責任保障大眾安全，若有人犯法，警方便有責任執法，以最低武力執行職務維持治安。<br />\n<br />\n多個婦女團體連同地區人士周五去信警務處長，譴責警方違反國際公約，濫用武力壓制女童、孕婦及女性市民。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網民：道歉真係咁難？<br />\n<br />\n不過警方回應未能平息眾怒，有網民留言批評警方欺凌弱小：「如果個小朋友係示威整傷就叫做自己攞嚟，但現在係俾警察整傷呀，個小朋友得12歲，你哋要執法無問題，但現在小朋友無犯到法又俾你哋整傷，同小朋友道個歉真係咁難？」"},{"pid":"2c8621fef327124176a1a98d2cabb27b3cbd10bf","tid":2200550,"uid":123848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:12:27.000Z","msg":"一律都喺最低武力，<br />\n強姦，暗角，槍擊，臭格。"},{"pid":"1f41253f27f736924ea9b24754e7c6a43a76e04f","tid":2200550,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:54:02.000Z","msg":"語言偽術<br />\n<br />\n本對係唔應該對佢地使用武力<br />\n<br />\n對佢地使用武力本身已經係犯法"},{"pid":"5c7734a92935df3648eb97bc6256da7e9ec73472","tid":2200550,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:54:58.000Z","msg":"佢哋唔出現根本好安全。<br />\n成日講大話！"},{"pid":"6e23f894316eac4fb0ef41fc83987a5978712904","tid":2200550,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:55:12.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好撚憎你地呀!"},{"pid":"671c437d337567db89a5fd3d07e5156f02f5777f","tid":2200550,"uid":254450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f41253f27f736924ea9b24754e7c6a43a76e04f","tid":2200550,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T05:54:02.000Z","msg":"語言偽術<br />\n<br />\n本對係唔應該對佢地使用武力<br />\n<br />\n對佢地使用武力本身已經係犯法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:00:35.000Z","msg":"會去到推孕婦落地，拖住細路女行，根本冇得拗。黑狗收收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}